{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban companies from charging more for products targeted to women",
        "additional_details": "I believe companies should be banned from charging more for products that are targeted to women as it is unfair. I think this is discriminatory pricing that is sexist and an economic burden on women across the world - especially as the gender pay gap continues",
        "background": "I want the Government to ban companies from charging more for a product that is substantially the same but targeted to women rather than men. This is also known as the \"pink tax\".",
